@Database Changes_To_V1.01.guide

@Node Main "Changes to HydraBBS between V1.0 and V1.01"

  Changes to HydraBBS between V1.0 and V1.01
  ==========================================

  Please read *ALL* of this file, or you won't know about some of the great
  new features of this release.

  Go on, it'll only take you a couple of minutes.

  This document is stored as HBBS:Docs/Misc/Upgrades/Changes_To_V1.06.Guide

  Details
  =======

  Sysop Information     - @{"More..." link SysopInformation}

  Developer Information - N/A

  Files Changed         - @{"More..." link FilesChanged}

@EndNode

@Node SysopInformation "Sysop Information"

  Sysop Information
  =================

  * @{"Bulletin Viewer" link HBBS:Docs/Doors/BulletinViewer.guide/Main}

    Updated example screens:

      HBBS:Storage/Example_Screens/Special/Bulletins_TOP.TXT
      HBBS:Storage/Example_Screens/Special/Bulletins_LIST.TXT
      HBBS:Storage/Example_Screens/Special/Bulletins_BOT.TXT

      HBBS:Storage/Example_Screens/Bulletins/#?

    Updated example config:

      HBBS:Storage/Example_Configs/Commands/All_Levels

    To enable the bulletin viewer for your users, read the @{"installation" link HBBS:Docs/Doors/BulletinViewer.guide/Installation}
    section of the BulletinViewer.guide file.

  * Control

    Improved reliability due to added stack checking and extension

    Bugfixes:

      - "ENV:HBBS_ScreenName" was not being deleted and was
        being appended to each time the Control was re-started
        or the screenmode changed!

  * Node and HBBSNode.library

    Added support for the DOOR_DisplayBulletin() function, which the
    bulletin door uses.

  * The docs for @{" Commands_system.guide/SystemDoorName_Type_XX " link HBBS:Docs/Configuration/Commands_System.guide/SystemDoorName_Type_XX} has been updated

  * Updated the docs for @{" screens " link HBBS:Docs/Reference/Screens.guide/MAIN}

@EndNode

